                                    </list_item>
                                </bullet_list>
                            </definition>
                        </definition_list_item>
                    </definition_list>
                </list_item>
                <list_item>
                    <definition_list>
                        <definition_list_item>
                            <term>To debug the <literal>app</literal> module:</term>
                            <definition>
                                <bullet_list bullet="-">
                                    <list_item>
                                        <paragraph>Open the <strong>Build Variants</strong> window using <strong>View &gt; Tools Windows &gt; Build Variants</strong> from the top menu.</paragraph>
                                    </list_item>
                                    <list_item>
                                        <paragraph>In the <strong>Build Variants</strong> window, make sure that in the <strong>Active Build Variant</strong> column, the <literal>:app</literal> entry is set to one of the <strong>Dev</strong> variants.</paragraph>
                                    </list_item>
                                </bullet_list>
                                <figure align="center" classes="figure-w480">
                                    <image candidates="{'*': 'engine_details/development/configuring_an_ide/img/android_studio_app_build_variant.webp'}" original_uri="img/android_studio_app_build_variant.webp" uri="engine_details/development/configuring_an_ide/img/android_studio_app_build_variant.webp"></image>
